sources.description:
The Moon Strikes Back | Impact | HD Sci-Fi Disaster Movie - After two scientists realize a rogue asteroid has struck the moon putting it on a path towards the Earth, they must put their differences aside and stop the collision or all of mankind could perish.

Watch Impact, a full sci-fi action movie where the fate of the world hangs by a thread. After discovering that a rogue asteroid has struck the moon and set it on a collision course with Earth, two scientists must put aside their differences to prevent total destruction. Perfect for fans of disaster movies, full free action films, sci-fi thrillers, high-stakes survival adventures, and planetary catastrophe stories, Impact delivers intense tension, explosive action, and a gripping race against time to save all of mankind.

Stars: David James Elliott, Natasha Henstridge, Benjamin Sadler
